You are working on a PHP scraping library for MMA data.

## Rules

- This is NOT an application
- This is a reusable library

## Architecture

- Scraper → Parser → DTO
- No database logic allowed
- No business logic allowed

## Source Isolation

- Each source must be independent
- Do not share parsing logic between sources

## DTO Rules

- DTOs must be immutable
- No logic inside DTOs

## Parser Rules

- Input: HTML
- Output: DTO
- Must be deterministic

## Scraper Rules

- Only fetch HTML
- Use HttpClientInterface
- Must be testable with mocks

## Testing

- Use fixture HTML files
- No real HTTP calls

## Forbidden

- No aggregation logic
- No deduplication logic
- No database logic
